---
description: Standardize generated plan documents in .cursor/plans with timestamp and version metadata
alwaysApply: true
---

# Plan document discipline

- For every generated plan document, store it under `.cursor/plans/`.
- If `.cursor/plans/` does not exist, create it.
- Plan filenames must include both:
  - current `package.json` version
  - creation timestamp in `YYYY-MM-DD-HH-mm-ss` format
- Each plan document body must include:
  - `Created at: YYYY-MM-DD-HH-mm-ss`
  - `Project version: <package.json version>`
- Treat `.cursor/plans/` as local temporary planning context (not for repository sync).
